  "prompt": "Someone deleted me on snapchat, so I deleted him & now he appears in my Added me section, but I cannot see his score. Does this mean he added me back?",
  "response": "If you see someone in your \"Added Me\" section on Snapchat but cannot see their Snap score, it typically means that they have added you back, but you have not accepted their friend request yet. If you had previously deleted him and then he added you again, you will see him in that section. You can choose to accept or ignore the friend request, and once you accept it, you should be able to see his Snap score.",
